{"tid":2055690,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"CCtai啲人有冇咁憎陳梓維議員呀。。。一有post話佢全部bot咁狗衝入去鬧。。。","createTime":"2020-06-08T06:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T08:11:00.000Z","uid":7439,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e37421075da83b7bb7ad26842de62a528ef2aa60","tid":2055690,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:58:49.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打知陳梓維去咗邊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2055673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2055673</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Le4pJdz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLe4pJdz.png&h=0c392646&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔通係妒忌10月11月打到飛天嗰陣<br />\n自己仲做緊冷氣軍師朝早送頭夜晚屌老母<br />\n冇諗過落街擺個易拉架做街站刷曝光率、比$3000按金就有得選、手寫政綱就可以見報、1124借東風就容乜易當選<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家嚟葡萄人<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"1000f4cf56f506b8547bb429837f3eb36f188aef","tid":2055690,"uid":7439,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:01:10.000Z","msg":"唔知佢做咗咩<br />\n唔識Google睇新聞 <br />\n唔識上佢Facebook睇吓<br />\n唔識PM佢<br />\n唔識打俾佢<br />\n唔識直接上佢辦事處問<br />\n唔識去區議會網站睇提案睇會議紀錄<br />\n<br />\n自己冇留意冇睇冇查以上資訊<br />\n就可以出post話人冇做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6e9ecf4e9f22a387a27d151f5c2ff3de0a9eab","tid":2055690,"uid":234509,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:03:43.000Z","msg":"Cctai<br />\n班人有冇資格投票都唔知啦<br />\n日日係度做鍵戰當抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe56328bd478da912e08c6a5246a5aed2ff9e7fd","tid":2055690,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:04:59.000Z","msg":"擺街站 呃like唔計啦<br />\n開會 本身要做唔計啦<br />\n直播現場 你食花生又呃like唔計啦<br />\n巡視區內設施 齋睇唔計啦<br />\n視察爆水管現場 咁係你整唔計啦<br />\n鬧民政署 鬧得罪人唔計啦<br />\n用自己